public abstract class GraphProcessorResource<P,T extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject> extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.resource.impl.ResourceImpl
Base class for resource which load their contents by creating a Stream of Element's from a resource URI and then uses ProcessorFactory to create Supplier's of EObject with ProcessorFactory.
